column2:
"Nah, I just can't get used
to calling you by your name.
Doesn't it feel weird somehow?"

"But whatever. Let's focus on the mission.
I want you to show me what you've got."

"Just see that you don't go back to being
the newbie and loser that you once were."

"うーん、名前で呼ぶの
やっぱり慣れないわねぇ。
なーんか気持ち悪くない？"

"ま、いいか。
それよりも依頼よ依頼。
アンタの活躍、見せてちょうだい！"

"へっぽこぴーに逆戻りしないように
頑張ってきてねー。"
